{"tid":2102794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【泛民初選】本土派素人聯合造勢 民主黨黃國桐撐新人馮達浚","createTime":"2020-07-10T17:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T03:11:42.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"871dcc2333f052444d2c82a7af08c79a3504818a","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"民主派今天（11日）將舉行立法會選舉初選，各候選人趁最後機會造勢，呼籲市民支持。參選九西的「九龍城大小事」主席<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">馮達浚獲民主黨九龍城區議員黃國桐現身支持，馮達浚相信自己與黃國桐政治理念相同，故獲「桐叔」跨黨支持，至於黃國桐則未有接受訪問。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有桐叔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200711/YSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2FYSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwummaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=1ab58e1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2FYSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=82dbbab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200711/YSSVXUV6A254D5W24UL5KUFNTE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"234b1adbbd997b1eea9c354c00a01315f614f433","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">本身為民主黨成員的黃國桐，並無支持同樣參與初選的黨友黃碧雲，反而現身支持馮達浚</span>。黃國桐未有在造勢大會發言，但在馮的宣傳品上，黃國桐形容馮是「有學識、理想和站在抗爭前線的年青（輕）人」，指他「不退縮、不變形，直至力盡倒下」。黃國桐又稱，「本土的年輕人經已成長，再不需要任何濫竽充數的所謂『代言人』」，呼籲選民全票支持馮達浚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桐叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫理不幫親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有桐叔支持，九龍西一於投馮達浚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f5dfc36937d492ee3790ed0be28c7bda82e42a","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:52:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd8e1ce6f12a483e7c17b4735bee2563da1c98b1","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20e0f1c9128964b9d4734f04d8ad33fb980dfec6","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1cf3e05355084e492dc759e236164eb87e62da9","tid":2102794,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"馮達浚點睇都正常過BIG雲啦"},{"pid":"aa780ddd0b7d137c5b43936b0dd87690da3b1176","tid":2102794,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟呢堆人投實啱，本土會成為主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6728922250c02c52ad9b3bcda2d5c9697742eab2","tid":2102794,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"桐叔好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97766e263d1bb819504f331ccc7a2d267509f49e","tid":2102794,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:03:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d3dc8839f2416bb88d8bf23968b0cfc7f12b518e","tid":2102794,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:03:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80fbed4328931bdd886e9a768f4228a0c2b9800c","tid":2102794,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fad9d72de20a9c07a10345c6b13802de16e42e27","tid":2102794,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"549eff041ecea307a0a51ed0f0d8d520625acd86","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d7aafced0231bcc3fd23f6f9d9e6ade6ca2d82e","tid":2102794,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3bf77a3d311e6c39bcff6638b30856c8c1fe3041","tid":2102794,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GC7vwZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGC7vwZA.png&h=6ce8ccd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbRzYEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbRzYEA.png&h=7d97804a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">九西初選 馮劉必投<br />\n踢走飯民 改革議會</span>"},{"pid":"9bd432c8da587078374b206c9c834eed160aea91","tid":2102794,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bf77a3d311e6c39bcff6638b30856c8c1fe3041","tid":2102794,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GC7vwZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGC7vwZA.png&h=6ce8ccd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbRzYEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbRzYEA.png&h=7d97804a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">九西初選 馮劉必投<br />\n踢走飯民 改革議會</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"呂志